cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with facial expression recognition in videos using 3D-CNNs, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of CNNs for recognition tasks also falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the challenges of recognizing micro-expressions, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the experiments involve the use of databases, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
